title: Bohemia Rhapsody
abstract: Johnny Fiama and Sal Minella performed a parody rendition of the song during the 2005 Jerry Lewis MDA Labor Day Telethon. Sal spills the marinara sauce that Johnny's ma FedExed to the studio, and Johnny and Sal sing a heartfelt apology to Mama Fiama to the tune of "Bohemian Rhapsody."
